## 步骤 5.5：写入构建交接文件

写入 `TASK_DIR/handoff-build.json` 总结构建结果：
```json
{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "source_phase": "build",
  "target_phase": "eval",
  "task_id": "task-NNN",
  "summary": "<构建了什么、CI 结果、实现过程中的关键决策>",
  "decisions": [{"what": "...", "why": "...", "classification": "mechanical|taste"}],
  "risks": [{"description": "...", "mitigation": "...", "severity": "low|medium|high"}],
  "open_items": [{"description": "...", "owner": "evaluator|builder", "priority": "..."}],
  "artifacts_produced": ["build-rN.md", "<新增/修改的源文件列表>"],
  "scope_changes": ["<与计划的偏差，或空列表>"],
  "created_at": "<ISO 8601 UTC>"
}
```

然后更新 `workflow-state.json` → `artifacts.handoff` 为 `"handoff-build.json"`。
如果 `workflow-state.json` 不存在，跳过更新。

## 步骤 6：提交

暂存并提交实现：

```bash
git add <specific-files-changed>
git commit -m "<type>(scope): implement task-NNN deliverables

Deliverables: (list what was implemented)
CI: all tests pass"
```

使用具体的文件路径 — 绝不使用 `git add -A` 或 `git add .` 以避免包含无关变更。
